Building on the phenomenal success of the adventure driving hit Crazy Taxi  comes the much anticipated sequel Crazy Taxi 2!
In addition to the familiar Limit Cuts and Crazy Dashes, Crazy Taxi 2  sports a wild hydraulic jump feature, a brand new traffic-jammed city  to navigate, and 4 new characters and cabs to choose from; each with their  own unique abilities and style. And if that weren't enough, now you can pick  up an entire group of fares instead of just one customer at a time,  allowing you to go for a huge payoff!
Crazy Taxi 2 - it's insane driving action!